{"type": "article", "id": 36030, "title": "Line的日本新年款有点萌，以及，戴森发布限量版中国红吹风机｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-26T02:35:11Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 253, "name": "LINE"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 16821, "name": "Vêtements"}, {"id": 36151, "name": "FOX Umbrella"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 104, "praise_count": 53, "image": "img/article/article_show/201612260858033MeY1kPXOxLQzAVj.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/legal/judge-lifts-injunction-carolina-herrera-oscar-de-la-renta-battle-laura-kim-10733472/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>为争夺人才，美国两大设计师品牌  Carolina Herrera 和 Oscar de la Renta 打官司</b></a> | 为阻止年轻设计师二人组 Laura Kim 和 Fernando Garcia，成为 Oscar de la Renta 的联合创意总监，Carolina Herrera 向纽约最高法院提起诉讼。Carolina Herrera 声称，其与品牌前高级设计师 Laura Kim 之间的竞业禁止协议依然有效，希望法庭阻止 Laura Kim 明年四月之前在 Oscar de la Renta 的一切设计工作。</p><p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/business/2016/dec/23/american-apparel-shuts-all-but-one-of-uk-stores-london-administration\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>AA 关闭英国的 12 家门店，裁员 150 人</b></a> | 继 American Apparel 申请二次破产保护，并且被加拿大运动服制造商 Gildan 出价 6600 万美元收购其分销业务之后，上周，AA 宣布短期内将关闭它在英国 13 家门店中的 12 家，并裁员 150 人。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/line-friends-new-year-celebration-products/\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本 Line Friends 推出了一系列新年限定商品</a>，仅限日本地区发售。其中，幸运物达摩和贺年果子系列将于本日发售。手捧布偶和招财猫系列部分已经售罄。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091550Wf3sBIR2rSowaMVZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091550mKIhuVTR6evaGYln.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091550V8lEwkNC5TDtdL47.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091557pzHE9Zc8W5JCfbVU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612260916058RCHSmdQvOJ9ihFe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091611l2fS3cQtLF5soVJr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091618jkzgdbsAuiI3YU9C.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091624Mc6w9OJ3vk0DYWT4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091632u19moFWZx8MYOTg3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016122609163224nrfWKxeStbidJO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091638WGv69QbafmJZwgs7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091638g4THfq9JFIhp2ZAj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">著名的英国制伞品牌<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/fox-umbrellas-x-roaringwild\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Fox Umbrellas，与国产潮牌 Roaringwild 合作</a>，推出联名雨伞系列。该系列雨伞包括三种不同材质的木质伞柄，伞面分别以黑色尼龙迷彩撞色、黑色尼龙、藏青色尼龙这三种不同配色加以呈现。售价从 1499 到 1699 人民币，<a href=\"http://roaringwild.net/STORE/index.aspx\" rel=\"nofollow\">限量</a> 80 把。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091651dynXpMmt6j1FP29O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091651WCzpKwZHlIeqyiMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091701I3LYdStbkWAN1FUP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091710kZgfOACPnr3e9GbI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091710nvzhU27XkfeybcmS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091719zIiDKjfn4dqpPaUr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.vogue.com.cn/living/news/news_17546632779121a6.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dyson 发布限量版中国红 Supersonic™吹风机</a>，这款吹风机将于 1 月 1 日正式发售，它还附带一个限量版皮革制盒子，售价为 3190 人民币。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091738ItKlbs2gAyc1Q7Ba.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/vetements-x-champion-activewear-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Vetements 与 Champion 的联名款现已上架</a>，延续了 Vetements 品牌一贯的长袖子和破坏细节。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091752BPOIWlgoXkqN3e58.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091802ZkR7eP6gLFuAXdiC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091802bjqrTDGZpCtzYIVX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091802YDXq62lG74x8ygiA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091802SXPY2UexZHIRkNqi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091802HcYdxEfnIhg045b8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091802PEvMmZeS57nNGDOr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612260918138FOs1pU2qyQrDZvm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091813dKGYShem6VDiWf5v.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">以在 Instagram 上面发布恶搞奢侈品牌而出名的艺术家 Ava Nirui，最近又发布了她的<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/ava-nirui-latest-bootleg-pieces\" rel=\"nofollow\">最新“联名”系列创作</a>。除了围绕 Champion 与各大奢侈品牌的联名之外，还包括 Playstation 与 Prada，Gucci 与 Nike Air Max 的联名，都让人眼前一亮。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091833BWqmThdKnOLecQ6f.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091833PgjcVnhoB2WdzflH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091833qn0G7mFKcUR2wV8H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091833qEY4FlrBItcNpdax.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091834iwHAnslJhXaOzp5E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091835KFRpBvQ5rx89n4OU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091835fk5cUGw8V234DlWu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091835g6loNMvTrzB2OJnb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091844ve5TsR3SqxtbPE6k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612260918449OEL4imUkVBTGCrj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/25/nikelab-air-force-1-animal-prints-pack/\" rel=\"nofollow\">NikeLab 出了动物印花图案版的 Air Force 1 系列</a>。该系列共包括四款不同图案的球鞋，将在未来几周内正式发售。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091902Dlx2cb3uJHgzi8Nt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702303\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091911YkETlqyBi4h8Svaj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702303\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161226091911oFN8vnb65mcYIgtG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702128\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612260919172WqslGjDQbhd8oV1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.702303\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://popbee.com/lifestyle/line-friends-new-year-celebration-products/\" rel=\"nofollow\">popbee</a></p>"}